Dhangadi transit matra hunthyo, airport le garda ...hehe.... Dherai ghumnai paidanathyo.... 

Mero chai praya jaso Pahadi bheg ka jilla haruma thyo posting.... Yo bhanda details chai nabhanum hola...haha....

Tyo euta sekuwa corner hunthyo Dhangadi ko.... sadai teta ka saathi ani colleagues bhet huda tetai basne garinthyo..... Rati sekuwa ani beer.... pheri sekuwa pack garera hotel ma lagyo ani pheri beer..... arko din tetikai bitne gartho....ani tesko bholi palta ta bihana ko flight....hahaha..... 

Charam jawani ka din haru, ani Dhangadhi ko tyo garmi ma pani, macchar le Malaria lagne dar le, baklo jeans ani full sleeved shirt lagaera pasina chuhaudai chiso beer khainthyo...haha.... 

Sayad tei bhaera ni hola Dhangadhi ghumna napaeko.... Female sathi haru huda chai, India Palia samma jabarjasti lagera janthe testo tantalapur gham ma.... Tyo gham ma Palia janu bhanda... euta chilled beer kholera basinthyo hahah...
